Product Description

Dora the explorer is taking your kid to school! This 14" Trolley School bag is a brilliant buy for your little one. This bag can carry a bit more than your child can. Simply fill up the bag and then watch your kid wheel it across the floor. And when he needs a backpack again just slip it over his little shoulder and he's good to go!
